  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3281706/" class="title-link">比较失望</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3281706"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/mesiento/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1945289-24.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/mesiento/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">月印</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-05-18"
      class="main-meta">2010-05-18 22:55:06</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3281706_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  我很少给书给2星的，但是我觉得这本书也就2星了。这书基本是百家讲坛型，不需要太深刻，有时候甚至觉得他举的例子非常糙，完全没有哲学家的气质。这是道德经的堕落。不如读原本。当然，这只是我一个的感觉，也许也有人还看不懂呢。适合领导干部企业老总买来放在办公室装13用。...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3281706/#comments">(5回应)</a>
