    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zzbd/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">卫画栋</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-12-26"
      class="main-meta">2009-12-26 18:59:32</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2891596_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  王蒙这老头子真能折腾，据说在2000年还得过诺贝尔奖提名，不过仅仅只是提名，诗人北岛提名次数比他多，连李敖的《北京法源寺》也提名过。若以诺贝尔奖衡量的话，他们都抵不过脱离中国国籍的高行健，《灵山》、《一个人的圣经》在台湾一出版，经法国那么一燥，咋就征服了诺贝尔...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2891596/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2891596_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2891596_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2126159">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2126159/" class="title-link">天地不仁</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2126159"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/4460490/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4460490-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4460490/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">私享会  up</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-07-08"
      class="main-meta">2009-07-08 18:40:07</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2126159_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  老子说：天地不仁，以万物为刍狗。王蒙的解读是：天与地是不讲仁爱的，它们将万物视如草芥——草扎的祭祀用的狗。王蒙感到老子的冷酷。于是我想，是呀，天地不仁，夺走了我的同学49岁的生命，在她可以享受生活的时候，让她饱受了折磨。我这么说，这么想的时候，多少心有余悸。...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2126159/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2126159_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2126159_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评18篇
                </a>
            </p>
</section>
    
